title: Did something happen to jungle recently?
body: I always queue as support primary, jungle secondary. I usually always get my main role. Today though I've been getting jungle more often than not! I never learned how to jungle, this sucks D:

replies.body: Yeah the "Fill" position now puts me into jungle more than support now lol. Wild aint it?
Some junglers are getting burnt out from all the changes. This is like Jungle v. 7, I think
